	<p><a href="http://www.thesteelwarrior.org/forum/showthread.php?t=7457" target="_blank">http://www.thesteelwarrior.org/foru...read.php?t=7457</a><br />
<br />
Cut and paste for your pleasure, sorry if formatting is borked.<br />
<br />
I dunno, the immediate items seem utterly craptastic to me  *sigh*<br />
<br />
Guess I'll keep my fingering hovering over the cancel button.<br />
**********<br />
Heres our new list we just got. This is NOT everything, this is what they'll be working on immediately:<br />
<br />
-potime fixes (not true instancing yet but a step -- i was told full instancing will take a bit longer due to having to make major changes)<br />
<br />
-raid message of the day (?***)<br />
<br />
-improving how soe handles beta and the testing process<br />
<br />
-increasing the number of debuffs allowed on a mob<br />
<br />
-increase buffslots on players through aa<br />
<br />
-note field on the raid window<br />
<br />
-improved consent (/consent guild) and drag. /consent raid, guild, or group.<br />
<br />
-improve corpse drag radius<br />
<br />
-make charms not no drop<br />
<br />
<br />
The "longer to-do list" - again, not everything but this is what they'll be discussing immediately:<br />
<br />
-back flagging solutions<br />
<br />
-improved raid and guild functionality<br />
<br />
-auto loot for your corpse<br />
<br />
-improvements to raid xp<br />
<br />
-no more alien NPC's (focussing more on familiar norrathian themes)<br />
<br />
-solo ldon-stle instanced or similar content<br />
<br />
-issues with item augmentations (also refers to focii/effects i believe)<br />
<br />
-possible enhancements to /guildwar<br />
<br />
and from the letter:<br />
Quote:<br />
Of course these aren't all of the ideas. You brought us a CD, 2 books, 20 printed sheets, and a manifesto. We'll need to go through all of those and our notes before we can really get a good tally of all the wonderful ideas and questions that were presented.<br />
<br />
There were quite a few other issues raised. The ones above are on a letter passed out to us at dinner. These were issues we brought up in our group discussions with the developers and Smed (there was 4? diff grps, ~9players per grp). But of course, i got some other stuff answered:<br />
<br />
-yes taunt mod boots work for warriors. It wil go to 252 just like everything else.<br />
<br />
- Probably going to be a way to see the time left on your buffs soon.<br />
<br />
-there is new armors coming to ldon, and the 1452 or whatever the cap is now will be raised.<br />
<br />
-augments will be removeable quite soon.<br />
<br />
-spell drops in god are being changed somewhat. Also quests to get some of the spells.<br />
<br />
-vp revamp coming very soon.<br />
<br />
-Much much much better CS is coming soon. Their csr tools they have available now are simply amazing. If you'd given up petitioning about problems, you should start again.<br />
<br />
There was just so much said/written down today that I'm sure i've missed a ton. I will say though that im pretty convinced this was not just a pr stunt.<br />
<br />
i tried to pk gilfalas irl too but then our dinner came and we forgot.<br />
**********<br />
<br />
<br />
Mach</p>
	
	
	
